This is a list of researchers in [[optofluidics]], a research and technology area that combines [[microfluidics]] and [[optics]] and has applications in [[Display device|display]]s, [[biosensor]]s, [[lab-on-chip]] devices, [[Lens (optics)|lens]]es, and [[molecular imaging]] and [[energy]].
